name: YDL
description:
Throughout most of my life, I've struggled to believe I deserve love and affection. After going through an incredibly difficult breakup, my inner demon is back to remind me that I don't. It's always there - in the corner of my eye, in the back of my mind, and looking back at me in the mirror when I am searching for answers. 

The answer isn't clear yet. Maybe one day it will be. 

(5000x5000px)
